*Istina* je da nikada ne znamo sve činjenice. (The truth is we never know all the facts.)

Svi misle da je *istina*, ali ja nisam siguran. (Everybody thinks it is true, but I am not sure.)

Ne želim da te lažem, *istina* je da se brinem za tebe. (I don't want to lie to you, the truth is I care about you.)

Oni su odbili da prihvate *istinu*. (They refused to accept the truth.)

Ljudi su poslušali *istinu* i pomogli svima. (People heard the truth and helped everyone.)